.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH add 1  "add " 
.SH NAME
add \- Add bookmarks to a collection
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBadd\fR [\fB\-\-at\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fINAME\fR> <\fIBOOKMARK_IDS\fR> 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Add bookmarks to a collection
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-at\fR \fI<AT>\fR
Insert at this position (0\-indexed); shifts existing items. Appends at end if omitted
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
<\fINAME\fR>
Collection name
.TP
<\fIBOOKMARK_IDS\fR>
Bookmark IDs to add
